rows.label: tlk45320123_05_msg0001
rows.name:
It feels like Alst's on the brink
of total warfare lately...

rows.label: tlk45320123_05_msg0002
rows.name: I can sense it in the air.

rows.label: tlk45320123_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I think something really
terrible's about to happen...

rows.label: tlk45320123_05_msg0004
rows.name:
I fear for my safety out here.
Maybe it's about time I filed
a transfer request...

rows.label: tlk45320123_05_msg0005
rows.name:
No no, I can't. They'll end up
putting me on the front line!

rows.label: tlk45320123_05_msg0006
rows.name:
Gah! It doesn't matter where
I go! I just can't shake
this feeling of unease!
